{
  "stem": "13258.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was one thing I felt because that was the first time I heard, really, shooting.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was-- heard the airplanes flying around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't-- on the first day, except for the artillery shell, I did not see any ordnance landing anywhere.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I heard it going all day long, from the morning when I got up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was frightened when I saw the people running away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a stream of people with hand wagons-- hand-carried wagons, and with horses, and without anything, carrying stuff on their back, and just going and going.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some probably had a idea where they were going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maybe they had relatives a little bit farther away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But nobody knew-- nobody knew that in the city of Katowice, where I was born, the Germans would be three or four days after the war had started.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At that point, if you didn't run fast, it didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, we were lucky at that point when we got out as far as we did get out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But people were trying to run away with cars.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they would run out of gasoline and would leave their cars standing on the streets, on the roads, on highways.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because there was nowhere to go anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "People would leave their belongings in their cars.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I know of friends and family who-- where the man, the, the father was a dentist, and one of the daughters was a dentist.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The father was abroad, and-- at that time in France, and ended in Portugal, and subsequently in Montreal, Quebec.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But the other daughter was with her mother fleeing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And and, and they, they left some of the gold in the car, which they had to abandon.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Dentists always used to have gold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they took some gold with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
